                                課程簡介
                            

                                 
                            

                                 
                            

                                Introduction
                            





                                本課程設計以數位學習之現況介紹與體驗，使同學瞭解實務發展；並以數位學習領域之重要理論及研究，使同學瞭解未來之趨勢。

《 課程簡介 -- English 》
                                This course is to introduce students with both academic and practical trends of e-learning. With the incorporation of the major learning theory and related research readings, students are expected to be familiarised with the theoretical foundation of the e-learning. Moreover, this course is to introduce novel information technology application in e-learning. Students will be able to equip with the practical skills of adapting e-learning technology for improving both their teaching and self-learning.











